    "name": "勇者莱斯之魔姬契约 Demo",
    "steam_appid": 3198810,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198810/extras/t0.png?t=1728741700\" /></span><br>《勇者莱斯之魔姬契约》是一款将RPG、卡组构筑与Roguelike融为一体的单机游戏。在缪斯大陆上，你将与最凶险的敌人斗智斗勇，解开男神之封印，击败女神，恢复世界秩序。这款游戏独特的三卡组战斗机制、契约系统和自由的卡组构筑，以及精彩的剧情故事，将为你带来全新的游戏体验。<br>【注】：试玩版包含正式版第一关<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198810/extras/869e219fec9cf7696e47f679d49039bc.webp?t=1728741700\" width=615 height=52 /></span><br>莱斯拥有独特的日牌和月牌，每种牌都有一套专属的战斗卡组。在战斗中，你将同时控制日牌和月牌，没有固定的套路，只有创新的组合。分享你的搭配经验，也许下一个强力流派就诞生在你的手中！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198810/extras/ff5654e5839839f43c4deb2ae23dacba.avif?t=1728741700\" width=615 height=346 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198810/extras/4735de194523eb94e1dc053462d099c0.webp?t=1728741700\" width=615 height=52 /></span><br>获取星辰牌只是第一步，释放星辰牌需要消耗不同的日月牌。在上阵限制下，如何平衡混沌卡牌和日月卡牌的数量，这是你必须斟酌的选择！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198810/extras/6df58546f1c1d6f4c5ae56ffae0711f3.avif?t=1728741700\" width=615 height=346 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198810/extras/4ca6dd991f094c9a86d2a56fe14953a1.webp?t=1728741700\" width=615 height=52 /></span><br>如果对战时的伤害不够理想，或者想尝试新的组合，你可以在非战斗状态下自由构筑卡组！但请记住，固定的组合并不能应对所有的敌人，灵活变通才能百战百胜！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198810/extras/491ca943844163787c446cf3eec70b59.webp?t=1728741700\" width=615 height=52 /></span><br>抽取多少牌？回复多少行动点？打出的手牌威力如何？你身上的契约直接决定了你在战斗时的各项属性。合理搭配契约，而不是追求最强，才是你获胜的关键！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198810/extras/235b3f7fbc6b350c6271cec0d417a107.webp?t=1728741700\" width=615 height=52 /></span><br>每个角色都有独特的剧情，随着游戏的深入，你将逐渐解开缪斯大陆之谜，完成你这次冒险的使命。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198810/extras/2fdfba76857d30293df0155c57c820bf.avif?t=1728741700\" width=615 height=346 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198810/extras/8540990c9c68bb0e8d16aaaf7f7eb3b5.webp?t=1728741700\" width=615 height=52 /></span><br>90+张日月星辰牌和混沌牌<br>40+个不同性格的NPC<br>40+个探索事件<br>100+个特色契约<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198810/extras/0fc1fb3288a89bf6074330aaa79152f9.avif?t=1728741700\" width=615 height=346 /></span>",
